ot;https://www.amazon.com/Anker-Charger-Foldable-Compact-MacBook/dp/B0CZ6LXL8R?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;亚马逊&lt;/a>;和&lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.anker.com%2Fproducts%2Fa2688-anker-prime-charger-100w-3-ports -gan%3Fvariant%3D43931966 079126&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F12%2F14%2F24320291%2Famazon-kindle-paperwhite-12th-gen-eufy-11s-max-robot-vacuum-交易-出售” rel=&quot;provided nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Anker&lt;/a>; 正在以创纪录的 45.99 美元（折扣 39 美元）销售 100W GaN 充电器，后者带有促销代码 &lt;strong>;WS7DV2FXJI84&lt;/strong>;。 Anker 的充电器足够薄，不会占用墙壁插座上的所有空间，但速度足够快，可以为几乎所有东西（包括笔记本电脑）充电。它具有三个端口（两个 USB-C 和一个 USB-A）来满足您的充电需求，并配有折叠插脚以方便存储。&lt;/li>; &lt;/ul>; &lt;aside id=&quot;EqqCbM&quot;>;&lt;div data- anthem-component=&quot;newsletter&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;slug&quot;:&quot;deals&quot;}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/14/24320291/amazon-kindle-paperwhite-12th-gen-eufy-11s-max-robot-vacuum-deal-sale" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/14/24320291/amazon-kindle-paperwhite-12th-gen-eufy-11s-max-robot-vacuum-deal-sale</id><author><name>昆汀·肯内默</name></author></entry></feed>